{"tid":2504790,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度海嘯疫情｜政府無能為力 民眾為至親乞討氧氣保命","createTime":"2021-04-26T06:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T09:45:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"43a14da1814af093cd8063f8ea78c31111739821","tid":2504790,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:51:42.000Z","msg":"艾哈邁德（Siddiqui Ahmad）夫婦帶32歲兒子阿布（Abu Sadat）來求氧。阿布的媽媽說，哪裏都拒收，無人幫助其兒子。他們和全國許多印度人一樣，只能靠以乞討借等方式獲得氧氣。<br />\n<br />\n阿布十分虛弱，躺在三輪車上迷迷糊糊，毫無反應，彷彿暈了過去。艾哈邁德請求義工協助，義工第一時間把氧氣樽拉過來，接駁喉管讓他吸氧。幾分鐘後阿布看似陷入昏迷，弟弟法拉茲（Faraz）擔心起來，不斷為兄心外壓。幸好，吸着氧的阿布仍然生存。雖然如此，法拉茲不時拍打兄長的臉頰，令他保持清醒，不想看着至親被病毒奪去生命。<br />\n<br />\n另一青年哭着找義工看看車上的兄長，幾經辛苦找到人來但已太遲，司機說：「他已走了。」<br />\n<br />\n這些震撼場面每天正在印度各地重演無數次，並無休止迹象。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210426/LJG3WGJH3VHZTMXTXWXZJWSMLY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210426%2FLJG3WGJH3VHZTMXTXWXZJWSMLY%2F&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepCEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=218f2bab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210426%2FLJG3WGJH3VHZTMXTXWXZJWSMLY%2F&h=e546aac4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210426/LJG3WGJH3VHZTMXTXWXZJWSMLY/</a>"},{"pid":"652fbb9d03b1b6c5c54df34ede0c72d31c93d793","tid":2504790,"uid":191300,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:53:22.000Z","msg":"原來個病毒已經進化到咁，睇怕要種多d樹先得"},{"pid":"88c5f12dd70dff775e2feb83e286b014b959caae","tid":2504790,"uid":343294,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T06:58:08.000Z","msg":"慘&hellip;雖然我成日笑9印度又污糟又多強姦，但咁印度今鋪真係大撚鑊，希望印度疫情快d完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb124b080def4035b1b6164fd1755bd1798e3eb1","tid":2504790,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T07:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港幾